examples.en: The old man was nodding in his chair.
The flowers were nodding in the breeze.
The old man sat nodding by the fireplace
examples.ru: Старик сидел и клевал носом у камина.

examples.en: “The bathroom is around the corner,” he said, nodding to the left.
examples.ru: "Ванная комната за углом", - сказал он, кивая влево.
